#include<stdio.h>

#define max(x,y) (x>y?x:y)
#define min(x,y) (x<y?x:y)

int main(){

int t;
int xll1,yll1,xur1,yur1,xll2,yll2,xur2,yur2;

scanf("%d",&t);
while(t--){
    scanf("%d%d%d%d%d%d%d%d",&xll1,&yll1,&xur1,&yur1,&xll2,&yll2,&xur2,&yur2);


    if((xur1>xll2) && (yur1>yll2)){
        printf("%d %d %d %d\n",max(xll1,xll2),max(yll1,yll2),min(xur1,xur2),min(yur1,yur2));
    }

    else   printf("No Overlap\n");
}
return 0;
}
